May be an image of text that says 'Sometimes I'd like to bring informational pamphlets and a slideshow presentation about ADHD to social gatherings with my kids, because don't think people understand that they're not ignoring instructions on purpose, and they don't mean to be "annoying." They're just not in control of their impulses, and their brains don't always retain instructions or rules, especially in an overstimulating environment. Please, keep inviting us. We're doing our best. Scary Momnng'.

May be an image of text that says 'The other day I was out with my 4-year-old daughter, and a random stranger commented on how she was "going to be a handful" because she was smiling and saying hello to all the guys. S I would pay to be able to see the look on his face again.'.
